***************************************************************************
Instructions on installing TAU can be found in the INSTALL file.   
JAVA users should see README.JAVA
***************************************************************************

Building and running this branch with soma-collector requires you to first set the
PKG_CONFIG_PATH to include soma-collector/install/lib/pkg-config. 

1. Configure TAU with the following flags: ./configure -mpi -bfd=download -unwind=download -mochi -useropt="-I/path/to/conduit/include
-L/path/to/conduit/lib -lconduit -std=c++14' 
2. make -j && make install.
3. There is no step 3.
